quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  27,36,"Tuma nde ɓe arnoo ka Sulaymaana, o maaki: "Enee, on ɓeydiray kam jawdi, kon ko Alla okkimmi, no ɓuri moƴƴude diini kon ko O okki on, ko woni, onon hoɗon farnora neldaari mooɗon ndin"."
  27,37,"Rutto ka maɓɓe, mamen ngaddana ɓe koneeli ɗi ɓe maraa feere muuɗum, mamen njaltin ɓe ton ko ɓe ja'asɓe hara kamɓe ko hoyɓe."
  27,38,"O maaki: "eey mon mbatu, ko hommbo e mooɗon addanta kam jullere laamu makko nden, ko adii ɓe arude ka am ko ɓe jebbiliiɓe?""
  27,39,"Ngaari jinna ndin wi'i: "Min, mi addante nde ko adii a immaade e darnde maaɗa nden, e pellet, min e dow ɗum ko mi cemmbuɗo koolaaɗo"."
  27,40,"Oon mo woni ka mu ganndal immorde ka deftere wi'i: "Min mi anndante nde ko adii a nde ndarɗe maaɗa ɗen ruttotoo e maaɗa". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde ko nde ñiiɓunde ka makko, o maaki: "Ɗum ɗoo, ko immorde e Ɓural Joomi am, fii yo o ndarndo lam si mi jarnay [mo] maaɗum si mi yeddat [mo], kala jarnuɗo anndu ko o jarni kon wonanay wonkii makko kin, kala yedduɗo kadi pellet, Joomi am ko o Galo Tedduɗo"."
  27,41,"O maaki: "Faytinanee mo jullere laamu makko nden, ndaaren si on annditat, kaa o laatoto jiyaaɗo e ɓen ɓe anndittaa"."
  27,42,"Tuma nde o arnoo, [o] wi'aa: "Enee, ko nii jullere maaɗa nden wa'i?" O wi'i: "Awi'ayma ko kayre tigi nii". Min ndokkaama ganndal ko adii mo, min laatii jebbiliiɓe."
  27,43,"Faddii mo, ɗum ko o laatinoo homo rewa ga Alla, pellet, kaŋko o laatinoke jiyaaɗo e yimɓe yedduɓe."
  27,44,"Wi'anaa mo: "Naatu ka huɓeere". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde o sikki ko nde duneere(tewru), o ñori dense (korle)makko ɗen. [Sulaymaana] maaki: "Pellet, ndee ko huɓeere newɗiniraande ndaarorɗe". [Debbo on] wi'i: "Jooma, min dey mi tooñii woŋkii am, mi jebbilanike Alla Jooma winndire nden, wond'ude e Sulaymaana"."